---
// CTA + Footer
---

<!-- CTA -->
<section id="cta" class="relative py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--color-primary-800)_0%,_transparent_60%)] opacity-40"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-[Sora] text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
      Empieza a conectar con el
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-400 to-accent-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        empleo local
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Crea tu cuenta gratuita y forma parte de la red de empleo más importante de Aguachica, Cesar.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://localwork.app/pages/register.html"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-400 text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-2xl transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:scale-95"
      >
        Crear cuenta gratis
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://localwork.app/pages/login.html"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white font-semibold text-lg rounded-2xl transition-all"
      >
        Ya tengo cuenta
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-8">
      Sin tarjeta de crédito · Sin compromisos · Datos protegidos con Supabase
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="border-t border-white/5 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <img src="/logo.png" alt="LocalWork" class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg" />
          <span class="font-[Sora] font-bold text-lg text-white">LocalWork</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
          Plataforma de empleo local diseñada para conectar a la comunidad laboral de Aguachica, Cesar.
          Patrocinado por la Alcaldía Municipal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm mb-4">Plataforma</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          <li><a href="#features" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Funciones</a></li>
          <li><a href="#how-it-works" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Cómo funciona</a></li>
          <li><a href="#roles" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Para quién</a></li>
          <li><a href="#stats" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Impacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm mb-4">Tecnología</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          <li class="text-sm text-gray-500">Node.js + Express</li>
          <li class="text-sm text-gray-500">PostgreSQL (Supabase)</li>
          <li class="text-sm text-gray-500">HTML5 + CSS3 + JS</li>
          <li class="text-sm text-gray-500">Supabase Realtime</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/5 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">
        &copy; 2026 LocalWork. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">
        Hecho con 💚 en Aguachica, Cesar
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
